      "raw_text": "The Spokane Falls h Northern is\nplanning to have q new sidetrack that\nwill be the longest and best on the\nsystem. The old grade of the line\nabove the junction is being repaired\nand new ties laid.\n\n\nThe enormous amount of lumber,\ntimber, etc. makes new track a\nnecessity."
